        </div>
        
        <div class="place-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-water" style="color: #00d4ff;"></i> Ooty Lake</h3>
          <p>Scenic artificial lake perfect for boating, surrounded by eucalyptus trees and gardens.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="place-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-mountain" style="color: #00d4ff;"></i> Doddabetta Peak</h3>
          <p>Highest point in Nilgiris at 2,637m offering panoramic views of the valley.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="place-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-leaf" style="color: #00d4ff;"></i> Tea Gardens</h3>
          <p>Endless rolling hills of tea plantations with factory tours and fresh tea tasting.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="place-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-tree" style="color: #00d4ff;"></i> Pine Forest</h3>
          <p>Serene forest with tall pine trees, perfect for nature walks and photography.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="place-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-water" style="color: #00d4ff;"></i> Pykara Falls</h3>
          <p>Picturesque waterfall surrounded by shola forests with boating facilities.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="place-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-spa" style="color: #00d4ff;"></i> Rose Garden</h3>
