            <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">üåÑ</div>
            <h4><h4 style="color: var(--primary-color);">Sunrise at Doddabetta</h4>
            <p>Breathtaking mountain views</p>
          </div>
          <div style="text-align: center;">
            <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">üçµ</div>
