      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--primary-color);"><h3 style="color: var(--primary-color);">Ready to Explore Ooty?</h3>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem;"><p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-color);">Contact us to customize your perfect Ooty experience!</p>
